name: FRP Holdings, Inc.
description: FRP Holdings, Inc. is a publicly traded real estate investment and development company based in the United States, primarily focused on the development, ownership, and management of industrial and commercial properties. Established in 1986, FRP has built a robust portfolio that caters to a variety of tenants, including logistics companies, retailers, and service providers. The company is known for its strategic approach to site selection, utilizing market research and demographic analysis to identify high-demand areas for development. FRP Holdings also engages in land development and improvement projects, leveraging its expertise in regulatory processes and sustainable practices. With a commitment to enhancing the communities it operates in, FRP is dedicated to creating spaces that are not only economically viable but also environmentally responsible. Their projects often emphasize modern design and sustainability, aligning with current market trends and tenant expectations. The company continues to expand its footprint across key markets in the southeastern United States, seeking opportunities to innovate and adapt to the ever-changing landscape of commercial real estate.
